{{#> base title="Reset Your Password"}}
    <p>Hello {{username}},</p>
    
    <p>We received a request to reset your password for your Adopt-e account. If you didn't make this request, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
    
    <p>To reset your password, click the button below:</p>
    
    <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="{{resetLink}}" class="button">Reset Password</a>
    </div>
    
    <p>This link will expire in 5 minutes for security reasons. If you need to reset your password after that, you'll need to request a new reset link.</p>
    
    <p>If you're having trouble clicking the button, you can copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
    <p style="word-break: break-all; color: #666;">{{resetLink}}</p>
    
    <p>Best regards,<br>The Adopt-e Team</p>
{{/base}}
